  "instructions": [
    "Press the tofu: place between paper towels, cover with a weight for 10–15 min, then cube.",
    "In a large pot, heat 1 Tbsp coconut oil over medium‑high. Add onion, garlic, ginger, and scotch bonnet pepper; sauté 3–4 min until onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika, allspice, sea salt, and black pepper; cook for 1 min to bloom the spices.",
    "Add tofu cubes, tossing to coat with the spice mixture. Sauté for 3 min.",
    "Stir in apricot jam, soy sauce, and lime juice until the jam melts and coats the tofu.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and coconut milk, bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer 15 min to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Increase heat to a gentle boil, then lower back to low, cover, and let the stew steam for 10 min without stirring.",
    "Taste, adjust salt or lime if needed.",
    "Serve garnished with chopped cilantro, a sprinkle of fresh thyme, and a side of steamed rice or flatbread."
  ],
